        school s5_0
            on s5_0.school_id=u1_0.school_id
    where
        d1_0.device_id=?

Hibernate:
    select
        d1_0.device_id,
        c1_0.classroom_id,
        c1_0.height,
        c1_0.room_name,
        s1_0.school_id,
        s1_0.ip,
        s1_0.school_name,
        c1_0.width,
        c1_0.x_coordinate,
        c1_0.y_coordinate,
        d1_0.ip_address,
        m1_0.manage_id,
        m1_0.manage_cate,
        m1_0.manage_num,
        m1_0.school_id,
        m1_0.year,
        d1_0.manufacturer,
        d1_0.model_name,
        d1_0.note,
        o1_0.operator_id,
        o1_0.name,
        o1_0.position,
        s3_0.school_id,
        s3_0.ip,
        s3_0.school_name,
        d1_0.purchase_date,
        d1_0.purpose,
        s4_0.school_id,
        s4_0.ip,
        s4_0.school_name,
        d1_0.set_type,
        d1_0.type,
        u1_0.uid_id,
        u1_0.cate,
        u1_0.id_number,
        u1_0.mfg_year,
        s5_0.school_id,
        s5_0.ip,
        s5_0.school_name,
        d1_0.unused
    from
        device d1_0
    left join
        classroom c1_0
            on c1_0.classroom_id=d1_0.classroom_id
    left join
        school s1_0
            on s1_0.school_id=c1_0.school_id
    left join
        manage m1_0
            on m1_0.manage_id=d1_0.manage_id
    left join
        operator o1_0
            on o1_0.operator_id=d1_0.operator_id
    left join
        school s3_0
            on s3_0.school_id=o1_0.school_id
    left join
        school s4_0
            on s4_0.school_id=d1_0.school_id
    left join
        uid u1_0
            on u1_0.uid_id=d1_0.uid_id
    left join
        school s5_0
            on s5_0.school_id=u1_0.school_id
    where
        d1_0.device_id=?
Hibernate:
    select
        d1_0.device_id,
        c1_0.classroom_id,
        c1_0.height,
        c1_0.room_name,
        s1_0.school_id,
        s1_0.ip,
        s1_0.school_name,
        c1_0.width,
        c1_0.x_coordinate,
        c1_0.y_coordinate,
        d1_0.ip_address,
        m1_0.manage_id,
        m1_0.manage_cate,
        m1_0.manage_num,
        m1_0.school_id,
        m1_0.year,
        d1_0.manufacturer,
        d1_0.model_name,
        d1_0.note,
        o1_0.operator_id,
        o1_0.name,
        o1_0.position,
        s3_0.school_id,
        s3_0.ip,
        s3_0.school_name,
        d1_0.purchase_date,
        d1_0.purpose,
        s4_0.school_id,
        s4_0.ip,
        s4_0.school_name,
        d1_0.set_type,
        d1_0.type,
        u1_0.uid_id,
        u1_0.cate,
        u1_0.id_number,
        u1_0.mfg_year,
        s5_0.school_id,
        s5_0.ip,
        s5_0.school_name,
        d1_0.unused
    from
        device d1_0
    left join
        classroom c1_0
            on c1_0.classroom_id=d1_0.classroom_id
    left join
        school s1_0
            on s1_0.school_id=c1_0.school_id
    left join
        manage m1_0
            on m1_0.manage_id=d1_0.manage_id

        device d1_0

        classroom c1_0

    left join

        c1_0.height,
        c1_0.room_name,
        s1_0.school_id,
        s1_0.ip,
        s1_0.school_name,
        c1_0.width,
        c1_0.x_coordinate,
        c1_0.y_coordinate,
        d1_0.ip_address,
        m1_0.manage_id,
        m1_0.manage_cate,
        m1_0.manage_num,
        m1_0.school_id,
        m1_0.year,
        d1_0.manufacturer,
        d1_0.model_name,
        d1_0.note,
        o1_0.operator_id,
        o1_0.name,
        o1_0.position,
        s3_0.school_id,
        s3_0.ip,
        s3_0.school_name,
        d1_0.purchase_date,
        d1_0.purpose,
        s4_0.school_id,
        s4_0.ip,
        s4_0.school_name,
        d1_0.set_type,
        d1_0.type,
        u1_0.uid_id,
        u1_0.cate,
        u1_0.id_number,
        u1_0.mfg_year,
        s5_0.school_id,
        s5_0.ip,
        s5_0.school_name,
        d1_0.unused
    from
        device d1_0
    left join
        classroom c1_0
            on c1_0.classroom_id=d1_0.classroom_id
    left join
        school s1_0
            on s1_0.school_id=c1_0.school_id
    left join
        manage m1_0
            on m1_0.manage_id=d1_0.manage_id
    left join
        operator o1_0
            on o1_0.operator_id=d1_0.operator_id
    left join
        school s3_0
            on s3_0.school_id=o1_0.school_id
    left join
        school s4_0
            on s4_0.school_id=d1_0.school_id
    left join
        uid u1_0
            on u1_0.uid_id=d1_0.uid_id
    left join
        school s5_0
            on s5_0.school_id=u1_0.school_id
    where
        d1_0.device_id=?

        u1_0.cate,
        u1_0.id_number,
        u1_0.mfg_year,
        s5_0.school_id,
        s5_0.ip,
        s5_0.school_name,
        d1_0.unused
    from
        device d1_0
    left join
        classroom c1_0
            on c1_0.classroom_id=d1_0.classroom_id
    left join
        school s1_0
            on s1_0.school_id=c1_0.school_id
    left join
        manage m1_0
            on m1_0.manage_id=d1_0.manage_id
    left join
        operator o1_0
            on o1_0.operator_id=d1_0.operator_id
    left join
        school s3_0
            on s3_0.school_id=o1_0.school_id
    left join
        school s4_0
            on s4_0.school_id=d1_0.school_id
    left join
        uid u1_0
            on u1_0.uid_id=d1_0.uid_id
    left join
        school s5_0
            on s5_0.school_id=u1_0.school_id
    where
        d1_0.device_id=?

        d1_0.device_id,

        c1_0.height,

        s1_0.school_id,
        s1_0.ip,
        s1_0.school_name,
        c1_0.width,
        c1_0.x_coordinate,
        c1_0.y_coordinate,
        d1_0.ip_address,
        m1_0.manage_id,
        m1_0.manage_cate,
        m1_0.manage_num,
        m1_0.school_id,
        m1_0.year,
        d1_0.manufacturer,
        d1_0.model_name,
        d1_0.note,
        o1_0.operator_id,
        o1_0.name,
        o1_0.position,
        s3_0.school_id,
        s3_0.ip,
        s3_0.school_name,
        d1_0.purchase_date,
        d1_0.purpose,
        s4_0.school_id,
        s4_0.ip,
        s4_0.school_name,
        d1_0.set_type,
        d1_0.type,
        u1_0.uid_id,
        u1_0.cate,
        u1_0.id_number,
        u1_0.mfg_year,
        s5_0.school_id,
        s5_0.ip,
        s5_0.school_name,
        d1_0.unused
    from
        device d1_0
    left join
        classroom c1_0
            on c1_0.classroom_id=d1_0.classroom_id
    left join
        school s1_0
            on s1_0.school_id=c1_0.school_id

            on m1_0.manage_id=d1_0.manage_id

    left join
        school s5_0
            on s5_0.school_id=u1_0.school_id

Hibernate:
    select
        d1_0.device_id,
        c1_0.classroom_id,
        c1_0.height,
        c1_0.room_name,
        s1_0.school_id,
        s1_0.ip,
        s1_0.school_name,
        c1_0.width,
        c1_0.x_coordinate,
        c1_0.y_coordinate,
        d1_0.ip_address,
        m1_0.manage_id,
        m1_0.manage_cate,
        m1_0.manage_num,
        m1_0.school_id,
        m1_0.year,
        d1_0.manufacturer,
        d1_0.model_name,
        d1_0.note,
        o1_0.operator_id,
        o1_0.name,
        o1_0.position,
        s3_0.school_id,
        s3_0.ip,
        s3_0.school_name,
        d1_0.purchase_date,
        d1_0.purpose,
        s4_0.school_id,
        s4_0.ip,
        s4_0.school_name,
        d1_0.set_type,
        d1_0.type,
        u1_0.uid_id,
        u1_0.cate,
        u1_0.id_number,
        u1_0.mfg_year,
        s5_0.school_id,
        s5_0.ip,
        s5_0.school_name,
        d1_0.unused
    from
        device d1_0
    left join
        classroom c1_0
            on c1_0.classroom_id=d1_0.classroom_id
    left join
        school s1_0
            on s1_0.school_id=c1_0.school_id
    left join
        manage m1_0
            on m1_0.manage_id=d1_0.manage_id
    left join
        operator o1_0
            on o1_0.operator_id=d1_0.operator_id
    left join
        school s3_0
            on s3_0.school_id=o1_0.school_id
    left join
        school s4_0
            on s4_0.school_id=d1_0.school_id
    left join
        uid u1_0
            on u1_0.uid_id=d1_0.uid_id
    left join
        school s5_0
            on s5_0.school_id=u1_0.school_id
    where
        d1_0.device_id=?

        c1_0.classroom_id,
        c1_0.height,
        c1_0.room_name,
        s1_0.school_id,
        s1_0.ip,
        s1_0.school_name,
        c1_0.width,
        c1_0.x_coordinate,
        c1_0.y_coordinate,
        d1_0.ip_address,
        m1_0.manage_id,
        m1_0.manage_cate,
        m1_0.manage_num,
        m1_0.school_id,
        m1_0.year,
        d1_0.manufacturer,
        d1_0.model_name,
        d1_0.note,
        o1_0.operator_id,
        o1_0.name,
        o1_0.position,
        s3_0.school_id,
        s3_0.ip,
        s3_0.school_name,
        d1_0.purchase_date,
        d1_0.purpose,
        s4_0.school_id,
        s4_0.ip,
        s4_0.school_name,
        d1_0.set_type,
        d1_0.type,
        u1_0.uid_id,
        u1_0.cate,
        u1_0.id_number,
        u1_0.mfg_year,
        s5_0.school_id,
        s5_0.ip,
        s5_0.school_name,
        d1_0.unused
    from
        device d1_0
    left join
        classroom c1_0
            on c1_0.classroom_id=d1_0.classroom_id
    left join
        school s1_0
            on s1_0.school_id=c1_0.school_id
    left join
        manage m1_0
            on m1_0.manage_id=d1_0.manage_id
    left join
        operator o1_0
            on o1_0.operator_id=d1_0.operator_id
    left join
        school s3_0
            on s3_0.school_id=o1_0.school_id
    left join
        school s4_0
            on s4_0.school_id=d1_0.school_id
    left join
        uid u1_0
            on u1_0.uid_id=d1_0.uid_id
    left join
        school s5_0
            on s5_0.school_id=u1_0.school_id
    where
        d1_0.device_id=?
